The paper discusses the scalability aspects of cell-free massive MIMO, which is a technology used in wireless communication systems. The paper proposes and evaluates a solution related to data processing, network topology, and power control. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.IT (Information Theory), which deals with the transmission, processing, and utilization of information. Other likely sub-categories include cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.MM (Multimedia), and cs.COM (Computers and Society).
